{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a29b39b771","title":"右派言论——反对社会主义民主与自由　赞扬资产阶级“民主自由”","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"12ad632405","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"a29b39b771"}],"tags":[{"id":"7aac50a8c5","name":"文艺战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"5378a8871a","name":"学生"},{"id":"5841b1c66b","name":"上海财经学院"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"c962143788","type":"title","text":"右派言论——反对社会主义民主与自由　赞扬资产阶级“民主自由”","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a29b39b771"},{"id":"d0daff0d73","type":"authors","text":"上海财经学院学生","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a29b39b771"},{"id":"c796e246ad","type":"paragraph","text":"(1)“现在没有真正的民主。”","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a29b39b771"},{"id":"9ce92c0d1f","type":"paragraph","text":"(2)“英国伦敦公园中各政党可以自由讲话，很民主。”","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a29b39b771"},{"id":"bcd15e9150","type":"paragraph","text":"(3)“过去英国有海德公园的讲台，任何人对邱吉尔不满都可到台上骂他，现在谁敢骂毛主席。”","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a29b39b771"},{"id":"537bc404b2","type":"paragraph","text":"(4)“共产党抓得太紧，言论不自由。”","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a29b39b771"},{"id":"330c068958","type":"paragraph","text":"(5)“毕业生可以不服从统一分配。”","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a29b39b771"},{"id":"aff167f368","type":"paragraph","text":"(6)“现在并不见得比国民党时好什么。美国好听苏联广播，为什么苏联和中国不能听美国之音呢?”","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a29b39b771"},{"id":"e2fbfae1af","type":"paragraph","text":"(7)“资产阶级议会可以象‘鸣放’一样，各人可以发表自己的意见。”","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a29b39b771"},{"id":"3f81ad89fd","type":"paragraph","text":"(8)“匈牙利学生有种，我国学生能如此做亦就有种。”","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a29b39b771"},{"id":"6d5d4a58ef","type":"paragraph","text":"(9)“人民政权是官僚机构。”","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a29b39b771"},{"id":"379b32ea67","type":"paragraph","text":"(10)“领导上已经把名单排好，叫我们划几个圈，这有什么意思?我们应该象资本主义社会选举一样自己投票。”","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a29b39b771"},{"id":"0c34ba1132","type":"paragraph","text":"(11)“不管在任何情况下都不应该先提名，否则就不民主。”","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a29b39b771"},{"id":"3badfd0d5c","type":"paragraph","text":"(12)“人民日报我相信，解放日报我不相信。”","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a29b39b771"},{"id":"092ae691fc","type":"paragraph","text":"(13)“我们报纸不真实，有欺骗性，对资本主义只登坏事不登好事。报纸上登的资本主义国家的新闻，有的似乎太可笑，如美国试验氢弹升上几公尺就掉下来。谁信呢?”","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a29b39b771"},{"id":"f220ef867b","type":"paragraph","text":"(14)“抗美援朝为什么报纸只登死了多少美国佬，而我国死的人为什么不登?”","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a29b39b771"},{"id":"c52eda8a96","type":"paragraph","text":"(15)“我国新闻还不够自由。”","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a29b39b771"},{"id":"a3ad543fbc","type":"paragraph","text":"(16)“国家不应封锁西方资产阶级国家的新闻。”","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a29b39b771"},{"id":"df25ba7ad7","type":"paragraph","text":"(17)“要求看香港大公报，为什么不准别人看外国报纸，这就是社会主义自由受到限制。”","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a29b39b771"},{"id":"b787b04cc6","type":"paragraph","text":"(18)“社会主义不如资本主义民主，国民党允许有新华日报，现在就没有别的报。”","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a29b39b771"},{"id":"026fe6d05d","type":"paragraph","text":"(19)“资本主义国家中有资产阶级报纸，也有工人阶级的报纸同时出现，可以自由争论，这样不是好吗?顶好象资本主义一样那就自由了。”","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a29b39b771"},{"id":"d4c08477de","type":"paragraph","text":"(20)“应该让大学生自由出版各种报刊，学术性文艺性社团也可以办报，到目前为止还没有看到一分全国性、地方性的学生自己的报纸或期刊，反映学生要求，代表学生讲话，并作为加强全体学生联系与团结的工具。”","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a29b39b771"},{"id":"1820b8b4de","type":"paragraph","text":"(21)“政治设计院很好，章伯钧提出很英明，党却提不出。”","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a29b39b771"},{"id":"ab8a79950c","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《反右派斗争言论选辑　第一辑　学生部份》（中共上海财经学院委员会编，1957年9","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a29b39b771"}],"page":{"id":"40fb9e598d","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a29b39b771","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}